NAME: Time of hospital admission
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is the Time of hospital admission

NAME: Not Specified
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is not specified or not received. If no Time Zero Event value is received, then this is the system default value.

NAME: Other
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is the some Other time value not in CV Terms.

NAME: Time of enrollment
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is the Time of enrollment.

NAME: Time of infection
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is the Time of infection.

NAME: Time of initial treatment
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is the Time of initial treatment.

NAME: Time of initial vaccine administration
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is the Time of initial vaccine administration.

NAME: Time of transplantation
DESCRIPTION: Time Zero Event (TZ0) is the Time of Transplantation.
